{"title":"D-69656","slug":"d-69656","positiveMarking":2.0,"negativeMarking":0.5,"timeMinutes":10,"questions":[{"statement":"<p>जर P ने '&times;', Q ने '&divide;', R ने '+', आणि S ने '&minus;' दर्शविला, तर&nbsp;खालील समीकरणात '?' च्या जागी काय येईल?</p>\n\n<p>94 R 16 Q 2 P 7 S 64 R 13 P 2 = ?</p>","options":["120 / ","118 / ","108 / ","112 / "],"answer":"4","explanation":"<p style=\"\"><strong>स्पष्टीकरण:</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"\">माहिती डीकोड करणे,</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\" width: 300px;\" width=\"396\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 79px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">अक्षर</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 79px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">P</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 79px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">Q</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 79px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">R</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 79px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">S</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 79px;\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">म्हणजे</span></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">&times;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">&divide;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">+</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">-</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/12/boadmas.png\" style=\" width: 343px; height: 179px;\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"\">दिलेल्याप्रमाणे:</p>\n\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">94 R 16 Q 2 P 7 S 64 R 13 P 2 = ?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"\">डावीकडून उजवीकडे चिन्हे बदलल्यानंतर आणि BODMAS नियम वापरल्यानंतर,</p>\n\n<p style=\"\">= 94 + <u><strong>16 &divide; 2</strong></u> &times; 7 - 64 + 13 &times; 2</p>\n\n<p style=\"\">= 94 + <u><strong>8</strong></u> <span style=\"\"><u><st