Normal\" style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-indent:0cm;line-height:115%;\nmso-list:none\"><span style=\"line-height:115%;mso-bidi-mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">11 &ndash; 11 = <b style=\"\">0</b><o:p style=\"\"></o:p></span></p>\nम्हणूनच, \"0\" हे योग्य उत्तर आहे."},{"statement":"<p>जर 'A' म्हणजे '&divide;', 'B' म्हणजे 'x', 'C' म्हणजे '+' आणि 'D' म्हणजे '-', तर खालील समीकरणात&nbsp;प्रश्नचिन्हाच्या (?)&nbsp;जागी काय येईल?</p>\n\n<p>114 C 85 A 5 B 4 D 33 = ?</p>","options":["151 / ","149 / ","138 / ","143 / "],"answer":"2","explanation":"<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">दिलेले समीकरण:</span> 114 C 85 A 5 B 4 D 33 = ?</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/07/62b6b038309f241e4e39e3b7_16572638863551.png\" style=\"width: 250px; height: 150px;\" /></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">दिलेल्या&nbsp;माहितीची उकल करु:</span></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 300px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">चिन्ह</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">A</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">B</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">C</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">D</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>अर्थ</b></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;\">&divide;</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">x</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">+</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\">-</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">आता, समीकरणात डावीकडून उजवीकडे चिन्हे&nbsp;बदलून आणि BODMAS नियम वापरुन, आपल्याला मिळेल:</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">नवीन समीकरण :</span> 114 + 85 <span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;\">&divide;</span> 5 <span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;\">x</span> 4 - 33 = ?</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">गणना:</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">&rArr;&nbsp;114 +&nbsp;<u><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">85&nbsp;</span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">&divide;</span></span></u><u><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">&nbsp;5</span></u>&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&times;</span>&nbsp;4 -&nbsp;33 = ?</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">&rArr;&nbsp;114 +&nbsp;<u><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">17&nbsp;&times; 4</span></u>&nbsp;- 33 = ?</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">&rArr;&nbsp;<u><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">114 +&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">68</span></u>&nbsp;- 33 = ?</p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">&rArr;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><u>182&nbsp;</u></span><u><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">- 33</span></u>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">149.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">म्हणून, योग्य उत्तर <span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">\"पर्याय 2</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">\"</span> आहे.</p>"},{"statement":"<p>जर &lsquo;+&rsquo; म्हणजे &lsquo;-&rsquo;, &lsquo;&divide;&rsquo; म्हणजे &lsquo;+&rsquo;, &lsquo;-&rsquo; म्हणजे &lsquo;&times;&rsquo;, आणि &lsquo;&times;&rsquo; म्हणजे &lsquo;&divide;&rsquo;. खालीलपैकी कोणते&nbsp;पदावलीचे मूल्य असेल?</p>\n\n<div>81 &times; 9 + 21 - 7 &divide; 147</div>","options":["6 / ","9 / ","294 / ","303 / "],"answer":"2","explanation":"<p style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><strong>दिलेल्याप्रमाणे:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); width: 150px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>चिन्ह</stro